      "text": "MOOCs are becoming more and more widespread and universities are interested in knowing the learning process of students in this format. The authors explore 2 distinct MOOCs and find common patterns when it comes to initial motivation and end of course attrition. However, when using more elaborate visualization the authors claim to have found meaningful distinctions between the courses. \n\n",
